---
title: Spiced Chicken and Pepper Stew with Garlic Rice and Soured Cream
description: This Spiced Chicken and Pepper Stew is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221215_R01_W04_UK_F12371-6_KB_Main_low-2d568917.jpg
